{"tid":2274090,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特首稱不會隨便回應港人解除檢疫訴求　冀內地居民放心","createTime":"2020-11-06T07:59:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T03:10:14.000Z","uid":60281,"like":10,"dislike":309,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd7f27953dd8f6f91f576664502e5ea6059b068","tid":2274090,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:59:42.000Z","msg":"香港特首?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥回應內地傳媒問到，內地很多反對放寬豁免14天檢疫安排的聲音，她回應，現時中港兩地需要14天檢疫安排，是為老百姓健康而設，兩地政府必須要在保障人民健康的前提下，才會解除14天檢疫的安排，香港不會因為經濟理由，隨便回應香港居民的訴求，不理會內地人民的健康，希望內地居民放心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558692-20201106.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558692-20201106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9nyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=7ae8738f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558692-20201106.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=69e1104a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558692-20201106.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"882caaf5f05453830f6558ff7bc67f6dba62e9b9","tid":2274090,"uid":228955,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"on 9"},{"pid":"15ecfaa33d5701e6d0db2547e46bfef6fd002603","tid":2274090,"uid":211827,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"真係痴鳩線"},{"pid":"db86bbbffc4246dc5673bc681210c2ea54a4ee26","tid":2274090,"uid":161726,"like":319,"dislike":2,"score":317,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"我冇呢個訴求喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咪封撚到死果日囉"},{"pid":"77943b22b0f34886e1007d25b3d14058fd5fca30","tid":2274090,"uid":356914,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:02:25.000Z","msg":"算啦 佢講野無人理"},{"pid":"5f9b4f4cec